# It seems there was an error during the extraction process, as well as when trying to insert the iron ore back into the stone furnace.
# 
# The extraction of iron plates was successful, but I mistakenly thought I had 5 iron ore remaining in my inventory. In reality, I only have 3 iron ore left in the stone furnace.
# 
# To proceed, I need to gather more iron ore to smelt into additional iron plates. Let's return to the iron ore patch to harvest more iron ore.

# Moving back to the iron ore patch to harvest more iron ore.
move_to(iron_ore_patch_position)  # Ensure I'm at the iron ore patch again before harvesting.
